{"tid":1186190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我已經知道美國點撚樣可以係一年之內ko 共產黨","createTime":"2019-06-04T18:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:06:23.000Z","uid":31637,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cde4ef262a8f7d37d9a643a7d8f1307ae582db42","tid":1186190,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"首先你要諗盡辦法引解放軍入港先<br />\n如果呢步做唔到<br />\n美國未必可以係一年之內ko 共產黨<br />\n如果做到呢一步，美國就有方法係一年之內秒撚柒共產黨<br />\n<br />\n詳細策略唔方便係度講<br />\n講完共產黨更加難中伏<br />\n其實出得呢個post 已經係博緊共黨線眼睇唔到，睇到真係咪撚幻想共產黨會派兵<br />\n<br />\n總之引到解放軍入港，一年之後就可以同共產黨講再見<br />\n<br />\n想香港輿論風向好d 可以諗下點樣唔會四面樹敵之下引解放軍入港<br />\n例如減少佔領區域，避免阻撚住班藍屍搵食，你一阻撚住佢地搵食，佢地就可以代替解放軍上前線<br />\n應該集中佔領有關大樓，癱瘓政府運作，立唔到法<br />\n迫共產黨出手，一出手就game over, 係共產黨game over"},{"pid":"6c56248c502e6c3eedd38178c86304670c7ba5f8","tid":1186190,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"若然屬實，天下之大妙"},{"pid":"4fca382008f16c24238f33527844622c7cd85e0a","tid":1186190,"uid":252312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"信住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d046db373699f0e6b6e76b8f196127472acc98d1","tid":1186190,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6/9，香港人，銅鑼灣見"},{"pid":"61c3093532c119268e3d8fc3ca6876ed1b3b51a6","tid":1186190,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:25:24.000Z","msg":"美國打共狗只需要3架航母就夠簡單輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4b49c46de9165f4b3f9cca0e2114013d9719a6","tid":1186190,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:26:11.000Z","msg":"解放軍本身咪注港囉"},{"pid":"64d08268c7511b6b3a84dc5ecaf73c19b4